title: Nathalie Bonnet
text: Nathalie is an environmental data scientist-in-training at UCSB who feels equally at home in the field studying pollinators and wrangling metadata in R. Beyond the keyboard, she’s usually chasing sunshine on a trail, bike, or surfboard.
